text: Park Kyung-suk is a South Korean taekwondo practitioner. She won a silver medal in lightweight at the 1993 World Taekwondo Championships in New York City, and a gold medal at the 1995 World Taekwondo Championships in Manila. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:South Korean female taekwondo practitioners Category:World Taekwondo Championships medalists
